<h1>Dashboard</h1>

<div>
<h3><a href="/dashboard/my-library">My library : </a></h3>
<p>You have {{stats.nbAllBooks}} book(s), among which {{stats.nbLendedBooks}} are currently lended.</p>
{{#unless stats.nbAllBooks}}
<p>You don't have any books in your library.</p>
{{/unless}}

{{#isEqual stats.nbAllBooks nbLendedBooks}}
{{/isEqual}}
</div>

<div>
   <h3><a href="/dashboard/my-borrowed-books">Books that i have :</a></h3> 
    <p>You are borrowing {{stats.nbBorrowedBooks}} book(s).</p>

       {{#unless stats.nbBorrowedBooks}}
<p>Currently, you don't borrow any books.</p>
{{/unless}}

{{#isEqualBorrowed stats.nbBorrowedBooks}}
{{/isEqualBorrowed}}

</div>

<div>
   <h3><a href="/dashboard/wishlist">My wishlist:</a></h3> 
   <p>You have {{stats.nbWishlistBooks}} book(s) in your wishlist.</p>
   {{#unless stats.nbWishlistBooks}}
<p>You don't have any books in your wishlist.</p>
{{/unless}}

{{#isEqualWishlist stats.nbWishlistBooks}}
{{/isEqualWishlist}}
</div>
